    "Typically, such datasets fall into one of two categories: (1) those encompassing drug pairs and their corresponding synergy metrics derived from various cell lines (in vitro screening experiments) or (2) datasets derived from clinical trials, where drug combinations are associated with positive or negative clinical outcomes.",
